title: Violet Marcel Cuckold
description: Bounce had a terrible feeling when his significant other Violet left him at home for her secondary school gathering. She'd been acting like a playful youngster all week; now, she won't much answer her telephone as he urgently tries to contact her. When she at long last gets home, she brought along an old pound of hers. What could turn out badly when your significant other needs to hang out with an old companion? Sway discovers that the sky is the farthest point when that old companion all of a sudden has an open welcome to stick his huge dark pecker wherever he needs to put it. Shouldn't something be said about Bob? He gets the opportunity to sit and watch while his significant other gets shook by a cream pie oldie but a goodie!
